  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for China Sustainable Retail Banking&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;As the world&#x2019;s largest greenhouse gas emitter, China&#x2019;s rapid transition to a low-carbon development pattern will require large-scale financing to achieve clean energy deployment and other climate change solutions. Bank capital pooled from individual and business savings represent an important source of funds that can be leveraged to invest in reducing GHG emissions. This work aims to demonstrate viable financing models and instruments that help attract retail bank savings and channel them to fund climate mitigation projects.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
